release_note: Added Personalized diary download on Lifemap menu fixed multiple accessibility issues and a few UI stability changes.

Addition of the sample data caused some confusion on recent initial sign ups of addition of sample events and bubbles i.e. daughter helped with a test account and said whats these events . The addition of sample events and bubbles to help how things work now have an overlaid image to highlight which are sample events bubbles data. Also all sample data can be added or deleted via a settings menu button... Also couple of bug fixes.

PDF Lifemap via email now available from Lifemap menu the main driver of me writing this app : . Sample data controlled Horoscope sign and Email SMS opt out for birthday reminders all added to settings screen. Few bug fixes.

Bug fixes and added sample data on sign up for new users to show how to use MapMyLife add remove in settings . Also added triggers on backend to help send emails on why and how to do stuff in MapMyLife.

Restructured settings page to not make mobile verification compulsory optionally used for SMS birthday reminders . Removed paywalls for now back in next major as they were getting in the way of feedback and bug fixes.
Added Shareable life questions with many RememberMe questions to share and add to events or journal on.

Changed from basic app purchase to in app subscription. Once logged in and on access to LifeMap menu item you will be prompted to subscribe and restore purchase if needed . Early access subscription prices of 2 months free and 2 a month.. Thank you for you support and welcome aboard.
